\c 4
\s UKhayini loAbela
\p
\v 1 UAdamu wasemazi uEva umkakhe; wasethatha isisu, wabeletha uKhayini\f + \fk uKhayini: \fl okutsho, \fq okuzuziweyo.\f*, wasesithi: Ngizuze indoda eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 2 Wasebuya ebeletha umfowabo uAbela\f + \fk uAbela: \fl Heb. \fq uHabela.\f*. UAbela wasesiba ngumelusi wezimvu, loKhayini waba ngumlimi womhlabathi.
\v 3 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kwezinsuku uKhayini waletha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni umnikelo owesithelo somhlabathi.
