\v 5 Kodwa uKhayini lomnikelo wakhe kayiwunakanga. UKhayini wasethukuthela kakhulu, lobuso bakhe banyukubala\x + 31.2.\x*.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuKhayini: Uthukutheleleni, njalo kungani ubuso bakho bunyukubele?
\v 7 Angithi uba usenza kuhle, kuyemukeleka\f + \fk kuyemukeleka: \fl kumbe, \fq kuphakeme.\f* yini? Kodwa uba ungenzi kuhle, isono siyacathama emnyango, lokunxwanela kwakhe kukuwe, kodwa wena uzambusa.
\v 8 UKhayini wasekhuluma loAbela umfowabo; kwasekusithi besegangeni, uKhayini wasukela umfowabo uAbela wambulala\x + Mat. 23.35. Heb. 12.24. 1 Joha. 3.12. Juda 11.\x*.
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuKhayini: Ungaphi uAbela umfowenu? Wasesithi: Angazi\x + Joha. 8.44.\x*; ngingumlondolozi womfowethu yini?
\v 10 Yasisithi: Wenzeni? Ilizwi legazi lomfowenu liyakhala kimi livela emhlabathini.
\v 11 Khathesi-ke uqalekisiwe emhlabeni okhamise umlomo wawo ukwemukela igazi lomfowenu esandleni sakho.
\v 12 Nxa ulima umhlabathi, kawusayikukunika amandla awo; uzakuba luzulane lomhambuma emhlabeni.
\v 13 UKhayini wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Isijeziso sami sikhulu kule\add ngi\add*ngakuthwala\f + \fk isijeziso sami: \fl kumbe, \fq isono sami sikhulu kulokungathethelelwa.\f*.
\v 14 Khangela, ungixotshile lamuhla ebusweni bomhlaba\x + 2 Kho. 13.23; 24.20. Hlab. 51.11. Jer. 52.3.\x*, njalo ngizacatshiswa ebusweni bakho; sengizakuba luzulane lomhambuma emhlabeni; njalo kuzakuthi wonke ongificayo uzangibulala\x + 9.6.\x*.
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Ngakho, loba ngubani obulala uKhayini uzaphindiselwa kasikhombisa\x + Hlab. 79.12.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibeka uphawu kuKhayini, hlezi loba ngubani omficayo ambulale.
\s Inzalo kaKhayini
\p
\v 16 UKhayini wasesuka ebusweni beN\nd kosi\nd*, wasehlala elizweni leNodi, empumalanga kweEdeni.
\v 17 UKhayini wasemazi umkakhe; wasethatha isisu, wabeletha uEnoki\f + \fk uEnoki: \fl Heb. \fq uHanoki.\f*; njalo wayesakha umuzi, wabiza ibizo lomuzi ngebizo lendodana yakhe uEnoki.
\v 18 Kwasekuzalelwa uEnoki uIradi; uIradi wasezala uMehujayeli; uMehujayeli wasezala uMethushayeli; uMethushayeli wasezala uLameki\f + \fk uLameki: \fl Heb. \fq uLemeki.\f*.
\p
\v 19 ULameki wasezithathela abafazi ababili, ibizo lowokuqala lalinguAda, lebizo lowesibili lalinguZila.
\v 20 UAda wasezala uJabali; yena wayenguyise walabo abahlala emathenteni, \add be\add*lezifuyo.
\v 21 Lebizo lomfowabo lalinguJubali, yena wayenguyise wakhe wonke olokwenza lechacho lomhlanga.
\v 22 UZila laye wasezala uThubhali-Khayini, umkhandi wakho konke okusikayo kwethusi lensimbi. Lodadewabo kaThubhali-Khayini wayenguNahama.
\v 23 ULameki wasesithi kubafazi bakhe: Ada loZila, zwanini ilizwi lami, bafazi bakaLameki, bekani indlebe ekukhulumeni kwami; ngoba ngabulala indoda ngenxa yokungilimaza, lomfana ngenxa yokungihluzula\x + Eks. 21.25.\x*.
\v 24 Nxa uKhayini ephindiselwa kasikhombisa\x + 4.15.\x*, isibili uLameki kamatshumi ayisikhombisa ephindwe kasikhombisa.
\s Inzalo kaSeti
\p
\v 25 UAdamu wasephinda wamazi umkakhe; wasezala indodana, wasebiza ibizo layo \add wathi\add* nguSeti\f + \fk uSeti: \fl Heb. \fq uSheti, \fl okuyikuthi, \fq omisiweyo, \fl kumbe, \fq obekiweyo.\f*; ngoba \add wathi\add*: UNkulunkulu ungibekele enye inzalo esikhundleni sikaAbela\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*, ngoba uKhayini wambulala.
\v 26 Laye uSeti wasezalelwa indodana, wabiza ibizo layo \add wathi\add* nguEnosi\f + \fk uEnosi: \fl Heb. \fq uEnoshi.\f*. Ngalesosikhathi baqala ukubiza ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd*.
